export default {
	updateAddress: async () => {
		const retain_keyPersonData = appsmith.store.keyPersonData
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_ADDRESS_LINE1 =vayNewAddAddr1.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_ADDRESS_LINE2 =vayNewAddAddr2.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_CITY =vayNewAddCity.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_DISTRICT =vayNewAddDistrict.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_STATE =vayNewAddState.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_ZIP =vayIndPinCode.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_COUNTRY ="IN"
		  await storeValue('keyPersonData',retain_keyPersonData)
		  return retain_keyPersonData
},
	updateEntityAdminAddress: async () => {
		const retain_keyPersonData = appsmith.store.keyPersonData
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_LINE1 =vayNewAddAddr1.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_LINE2 =vayNewAddAddr2.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_CITY =vayNewAddCity.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_DISTRICT =vayNewAddDistrict.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_STATE =vayNewAddState.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_ZIP =vayIndPinCode.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_COUNTRY ="IN"
		  await storeValue('keyPersonData',retain_keyPersonData)
		  return retain_keyPersonData
}
	
}
